# One scene, a whole wardrobe. `foley` is the house dress: the brand's
# own film world — celluloid margin, warm near-black screen, REC-red
# cursor, and a palette whose bright magenta doubles as the keys reel's
# accent. VHS ignores the cue below and still records this tape.

Output foley.gif
# foley: dress foley

Set Width 700
Set Height 340
Set FontSize 16
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "echo 'same tape, dressed as: foley'"
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
Type "seq 1 3"
Enter
Sleep 2s
